    "description": "Beauty Kadan Holdings Co., Ltd. engages in the planning, production, and installation of fresh flower altars in Japan and internationally. The company operates through three segments: Flower Altar Business, Bridal Flower Arrangement Business, and Fresh Flower Wholesale Business. It also produces and sells wedding flower products, such as Takasago flowers, table flowers, and bouquets, including setup; and supplies fresh flower to funeral-related companies and fresh flower retailers; engages in planning and consulting services for weddings, funerals, and other ceremonies; employment support business; agriculture; restaurants continuation support business; and the manufacture and sale of fertilizers, as well as system development business. The company was formerly known as Beauty Kadan Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Beauty Kadan Holdings Co., Ltd. in August 2023. Beauty Kadan Holdings Co., Ltd. was founded in 1974 and is headquartered in Kumamoto, Japan."
